{"tid":23363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山男跣腳墮山澗","createTime":"2016-12-05T01:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T01:30:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e29fa3ca3275745422f26144073533b6abecc245","tid":23363,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:28:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19855293&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19855293%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161205&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0c371602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19855293%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161205&h=634afdad\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19855293&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161205</a><br />\n<br />\n行山男跣腳墮山澗<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■行山男墮澗受傷，由消防員救出送院治理。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】4名男女昨晨結伴往渣甸山郊遊，其間行上畢拉山道，惟經過一條溪澗時，其中一名行山漢跣腳，跌落2米下的溪澗，右腳及腰背受傷，當場動彈不得，同行友人見狀慌忙報警求助，消防員及救護員接報到場搜救，花約2小時將事主抬救至大坑徑，他當時清醒，其後送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n事主姓陳（56歲），昨晨11時許，他與兩男一女友人行山，各人先由虎豹別墅起步，計劃行至畢拉山道，行了約一半路程時，陳突然跣腳跌落2米下的溪澗，右腳及腰背受傷，痛極呼叫，同行友人見狀立即報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n消防員及救護員接報到場，帶齊裝備上山搜救，花約2小時，直至下午1時許，消防員將陳抬救至大坑徑，為他固定受傷部位後，再由救護車送院，陳當時清醒，狀甚痛楚，送院時由同行女友人陪同。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉永明<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;團體促縮窄元朗單車徑救數百樹<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;【蘋果照相機】假日動與靜"},{"pid":"265b96862e187eec4ce6b5ba53b7955701c31298","tid":23363,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161205/280pix/05la5p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161205%2F280pix%2F05la5p5.jpg&h=2bbcbfee&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}